    "body_html": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-collapse:collapse;caption-side:bottom;background-color: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 0;\" data-oe-version=\"1.0\">\n  <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding: 20px 0;\">\n        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-collapse:collapse;caption-side:bottom;max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; color: #101820; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n          <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:solid;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;border-left-color:inherit;border-bottom-color:inherit;border-right-color:inherit;border-top-color:inherit;padding: 20px;\">\n\n                \n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin: 0; padding: 0;\">\n                  Dear <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"object.partner_name or 'Applicant'\"/></b>,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  Thank you for taking the time to connect with us regarding the \n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"object.job_id.name or 'Position'\"/></b> role at \n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'BICC'\"/></b>.\n                </p>\n\n                \n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n                  We understand that career paths can change, and we respect your decision to step away from this opportunity.\n                  While we regret that we won\u2019t have the chance to move forward together at this time, we truly appreciate \n                  your interest and the effort you put into the process.\n                </p>\n\n                <!-- Encouragement -->\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n                  Should you reconsider in the future or wish to explore other roles with us, we encourage you to stay connected.\n                  Our doors remain open, and we\u2019d love to hear from you again if a future opportunity aligns with your goals.\n                </p>\n\n                <!-- Closing -->\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n                  We wish you the best of luck in your career journey and hope our paths cross again soon.\n                </p>\n\n                <!-- Divider -->\n                <hr width=\"97%\" style=\"border-style:none;border-top-width:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #101820; border: none; background-color: #ec008c; height: 1px; margin: 16px 0px; opacity: 0.7;\"/>\n\n                <!-- Footer -->\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:20px 0 16px 0;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin-top: 20px;\">\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">The Recruitment Team</b><br/>\n                  <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name or 'BICC'\"/><br/>\n                  <a t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;text-decoration: none; color: #374151;\">\n                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.website or ''\"/>\n                  </a>\n                </p>\n\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n",
